                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7672" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0782</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">4353 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">向“绿”而生，处处花飞：云铝股份绿色发展的创新实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Growing towards &quot;Green&quot; and Flying Everywhere: Innovative Practice of Green Development of Yunnan Aluminum Corporation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王伦，周羽中（通讯作者），张诗含，王亚之，张智敏，邹娜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南铝业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云铝股份；重污染企业；绿色发展；创新实践；2023百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yunnan Aluminum Corporation; Heavy polluting enterprises; Green development; Innovative Practice</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">实现碳达峰、碳中和是解决资源约束问题、推进全球气候治理、构建人类命运共同体的重要支撑，因此绿色低碳成为企业未来发展的主旋律。本案例以云铝股份为例，呈现了作为重污染却又天生绿色化企业的云铝股份，以产品研发为核心进行绿色技术创新，以绿色技术为基础形成绿色一体化产业链，最终打造出“绿色铝•在云铝”的行业金字招牌，实现了经济社会效益和绿色生态效益双赢的过程。通过本案例的学习，帮助学生了解企业绿色创新的丰富内涵，指引学生探索企业实施绿色低碳发展的动因、方式和效应，从而加深学生对企业绿色低碳发展的认识。同时，为同行业企业的绿色低碳发展提供经验借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Achieving carbon peak and carbon neutrality is an important support for solving resource constraints, promoting global climate governance, and building a community with a shared future for mankind. Therefore, green and low-carbon has become the theme of future development of enterprises. This case takes Yunnan Aluminum Corporation as an example to demonstrate that Yunnan Aluminum Corporation, as a heavily polluting enterprise, focuses on product research and development for green technology innovation, forms a green integrated industrial chain based on green technology, and ultimately creates a golden brand of &quot;Green Aluminum in Yunnan Aluminum&quot;, achieving a win-win situation of economic and social benefits and green ecological benefits. Through this case study, we aim to help students understand the rich connotations of green innovation in enterprises, guide them to explore the motivations, methods, and effects of implementing green and low-carbon development in enterprises, and deepen their understanding of green and low-carbon development in enterprises. At the same time, provide experience and reference for the green and low-carbon development of enterprises in the same industry. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业绿色创新战略的驱动因素;绿色创新的内涵、维度;绿色创新实践的挑战和应对措施;绿色创新绩效的维度;</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
